In this video, Bright Djampa (CEO & Founder of OMEGA3) shares how upgrading to the oilless Kaeser i.Comp improved his production, allowing his team to manufacture 1.5 million units a month. See how Kaeser’s KAirFree program helped OMEGA3 achieve a completely worry-free compressed air solution.

@eatomega3
#compressedairasaservice #kairfree #customertestimonial

