@troyleedesigns is recognized worldwide as the premier custom helmet paint shop, supplying top-tier motocross and mountain bike gear to the fastest racers on the planet. When your reputation relies on flawless quality, you can't afford second-best equipment.

That’s why Troy has trusted Kaeser Compressors for over 10 years to power his paint booths, and why he just added a second Kaeser compressor to support their expanding operations!

#troyleedesigns #shopcompressor #kaesercompressors #testimonial
